Package: wetlandtools
Title: Wetland Field Data Analysis Tools for Alberta
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Iain", "Sharp", email = "iain@greenplan.ca",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of tools for ingesting, validating, transforming, and
    visualizing wetland field data collected in Alberta. Supports vegetation,
    soils, and water permanence analyses aligned with Alberta-specific regulatory
    frameworks including ABWRET-A, WAIR, and the ANPC Wetland Classification
    System. Intended for use in producing technical reports for regulatory
    submissions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
